
Overview of noun assessment

The noun assessment has 4 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (4) appraisal, assessment -- (the classification of someone or something with respect to its worth)
2. assessment -- (an amount determined as payable; "the assessment for repairs outraged the club's membership")
3. assessment -- (the market value set on assets)
4. judgment, judgement, assessment -- (the act of judging or assessing a person or situation or event; "they criticized my judgment of the contestants")
